<l>aṟattāṟṟi ṉilvāḻkkai yāṟṟiṟ puṟattāṟṟiṟ</l>
<l> pōoyp peṟuva tevaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What will he who lives virtuously in the domestic state gain by going into the other, (ascetic) state ?</l>
